  "title": "Japanese Speaking Commercial School Teacher",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for Japanese speaking tutor who can teach students from pre-school to highschool for the subjects of Japanese, English, Humanities at a commercial school catered for Japanese students who attend Japanese school in Singapore.</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Teaching Japanese and classical Japanese to pre-school, primary students, secondary, high school students.</li>\n  <li>Teaching English grammar, comprehension, essay writing and vocabulary to primary, secondary, high school students.</li>\n  <li>Teaching Humanities (history, geography) to secondary school students.</li>\n  <li>Creating and designing curriculum, teaching materials for Japanese and English subjects.</li>\n  <li>Meeting with parents and conversing in Japanese language.</li>\n  <li>Handling telephone calls and email correspondence in Japanese language.</li>\n  <li>Creating test problems and test data managing for students.</li>\n</ul>",
